japan januari industri product revi up japan 's januari season adjust industri product index ( base 1980 ) wa revi upward to 122.3 from a preliminari 122.0 , the ministri of intern trade and industri said . the revi adjust januari index wa down 0.5 pct from decemb when it rose 3.6 pct from a month earlier . the revi unadjust januari index rose 0.5 pct from a year earlier , after a one pct year-on-year decemb rise . the adjust produc ' shipment index ( base 1980 ) for januari wa revi upward to 117.7 from a preliminari 117.4. the index wa down 0.7 pct from decemb when it rose three pct from a month earlier . the revi unadjust index wa up 1.0 pct from a year earlier after a 1.4 pct year-on-year decemb rise . the adjust index of produc ' inventori of finish good ( base 1980 ) for januari wa unchang from a preliminari 105.9. the index wa down 0.3 pct from decemb when it rose 1.1 pct . unadjust , the revi index wa down 2.3 pct from a year earlier after a 2.1 pct year-on-year drop in decemb .